29:15.720 --> 29:23.720
B2C is a market where goods are supplied and sold for subsequent acquisition.

29:23.720 --> 29:32.720
Let's take a look at a minibus that can be found on two markets.

29:32.720 --> 29:38.720
If I buy a minibus for myself, for my family, to travel, to go fishing.

