32:40.720 --> 32:47.720
or in the case of exchange goods, where it is impossible to set distinctive characteristics of the product.

32:48.720 --> 32:49.720
Target marketing.

32:49.720 --> 32:55.720
In this case, we aim to influence a certain target group of consumers,

32:55.720 --> 33:01.720
