33:18.720 --> 33:26.720
For example, Harley Davidson motorcycles are nothing more than marketing at the level of market niches.

33:26.720 --> 33:31.720
That is, consumers of this product feel the need not only in the means of transportation,

33:31.720 --> 33:34.720
but also in the image of the purchased product.

33:35.720 --> 33:39.720
At the same time, the capacity of the segment or niche,

33:39.720 --> 33:47.720
on which Harley Davidson operates in relation to the entire motorcycle market is extremely small.

33:47.720 --> 33:51.720
Micromarketing, or marketing of one person.

33:51.720 --> 33:56.720
This is, as many experts say, the future of marketing.

33:56.720 --> 34:04.720
That is, in the near future, all goods and services will be produced for the needs of one individual.

34:04.720 --> 34:10.720
