01:31:03.720 --> 01:31:05.720
Going beyond the limits of the industry, looking wider,

01:31:06.720 --> 01:31:08.720
you can become the best of your industry.

01:31:09.720 --> 01:31:12.720
Therefore, comparing to your industry is not all.

01:31:13.720 --> 01:31:17.720
